### created: 2020-Jan-03
### updated: 2024-Jan-01  Happy New Year!
###
### man sunclock
###
### This config file is for when I execute sunclock as a
### "screensaver", though I liken it more to Live Wallpaper.
###
###=================================================================
###
aspect 0
bottomline
#city Philadelphia
citymode 0
classname sunclock-mini
colorlevel 3
darkness 0.85
fillmode 2
#fixedrootpos
language: en
map
mapgeom 450x225
mapmode E
meridianmode 3
### meridianspacing is not working for values higher than 30
#meridianspacing 90
moon
parallelmode 0
position 39.960|-75.170
### Lower right: rootdx of 1 and rootdy of 0.9
#rootdx 1.00
#rootdy 0.90
rootperiod 120
setcolor mapstripbg|White
setcolor mark1|green
setcolor root|Black
setcolor star|Black
### Looking for fonts? Execute: xfontsel -or- xlsfonts -- not fc-list or font-manager
setfont coord|lucidasanstypewriter-bold-12
setfont mapstrip|-*-times-bold-r-*-*-12-*-*-*-*-*-*-*
#screensaver
shading 4
sun
tropics
vmfflags 2
###=================================================================
#EOF
